  whether the Member State has clearly indicated what pressure(s) the measure
  addresses. The assessor should cross-check this information with the
  information reported under Article 8 to verify they are consistent. However,
  the way pressures are addressed in Art 8 is quite generic, just listing the
  type of pressure from the enumeration list &ndash; see table below.
</p>
